description:
Meet the exciting parking simulator with drawing!

In front of you is a city parking filled with various obstacles. Draw a route for your car in such a way as to avoid all obstacles and park the car at the desired parking point.

Sound simple? Yes, but in reality, various obstacles and traps will greatly interfere with you, so you will have to strain your attention and correctly calculate the trajectory of movement. If there are no big problems with fixed obstacles, then moving obstacles will make the driver sweat!

Key features:
• Excellent workout for the mind and logic;
• Lots of levels with different difficulty;
• Addictive gameplay for all ages;
• Management with the Joy-Con™️ controllers;
• Relaxing musical accompaniment;
